Washington, D.C.; About Narrator: No info provided.; Collection:U004 BASEMENT Room 024: Southwest Oral Histor ; Notes:Ben Nighthorse Campbell and Michael Anderson, the Director of the National Congress of American Indians, are interviewed by answering call-in questions about such issues like H.U.D., Native sovereignty, Alaskan corporations, political reality, jurisdiction problems, and gambling issues, etc.;

