Political parties--Colorado--1995
Legislators--United States--1995
Washington, D.C.; About Narrator: No info provided.; Collection:U004 BASEMENT Room 024: Southwest Oral Histor ; Notes:Ben N. Campbell is asked about his senatorial routines and his switching of political parties. Other topics include public land policies, the proposed balanced budget amendment, and the Contract for America. Other guests on the episode: Michelle Davis of the majority leader's office, Dave Hoppe of the majority whip's office, Bill Hoagland, and Bob Stevenson. ;

